<template>
  <v-app>
    <v-navigation-drawer app permanent>
      <v-list>
        <v-list-item v-for="category in categories" :key="category">
          <v-list-item-content>
            <v-list-item-title>{{ category }}</v-list-item-title>
          </v-list-item-content>
        </v-list-item>
      </v-list>
    </v-navigation-drawer>
    
    <v-main>
      <!-- 나머지 내용 -->
    </v-main>
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      categories: ["식품", "전자제품", "도서", "의류"]
    };
  }
};
</script>

<style>
/* 추가적인 스타일링을 할 수 있습니다. */
</style>
